<br>
The way I start healing against Sont/Kland is by CCing the lowest HP player in my group. Then followed with a SH on the next lowest HP person. Continue that way until everyone is down 3 1/2 bubbs. Then enough time has passed to make HWoP an option against those two. <br>
<br>
Most other mobs are not that bad in regards to heal aggro but still wait to cast the first HWoP until everyone is kindof at 3 1/2 bubbs of health.<br>
<br>
With time you pretty much know when HWoP is safe to cast and when you are know you get insta aggro. =)<br>
