Since this is a Paladin only spell (not a cleric hand-me-down), I find it hard to believe they didn't design the spell with the healing penalty in mind.  What makes you think they didn't say &quot;I think it should heal 594 so therefore we'll make it 660 so that with the healing penalty it works out that way.&quot;?<br>
<br>
Personally I'm happy with the heal/mana ratio of HWoP. <p><BR>
